doc.previous: Boeing Launch Services Inc BLS is Boeing s commercial launch service provider On behalf of its commercial customers BLS administers launch service contracts for Delta II and Delta IV launches conducted by United Launch Alliance In November 2010 Boeing Defense Space Security was selected by NASA for consideration for potential contract awards for heavy lift launch vehicle system concepts and propulsion technologies 11
doc.after: On July 21 2006 Boeing announced that it would be consolidating its Southern California locations The Boeing facility in Anaheim will be moving to Huntington Beach California 12
